{"tid":572276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)中央建議修憲增設國家監察委員會","createTime":"2018-02-25T12:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T15:59:28.000Z","uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1350915ef212048686f9f271c6c923e8d89cfed9","tid":572276,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"25.02.2018 17:56<br />\n<br />\n中共中央委員會修憲內容建議，在國家機構架構中，增設國家監察委員會，成為國家最高監察機關，領導地方各級監察委員會的工作，對全國人民代表大會和全國人民代表大會常務委員會負責。<br />\n<br />\n國監委依照法律規定獨立行使監察權，不受行政機關、社會團體和個人的干涉。監察機關辦理職務違法和職務犯罪案件，應當與審判機關、檢察機關、執法部門互相配合，互相制約。建議中的國監委將由一名主任領導，並設副主任及委員若干人。國監委主任的任期，與當屆人大任期相同，連續任職不得超過兩屆。"},{"pid":"d61b80e23ce37d3219dc102b3dc3df3262ba112a","tid":572276,"uid":42580,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"東廠"},{"pid":"eb09bb3c2e791baee63e1cd313df8263cc7d768c","tid":572276,"uid":127123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"委員會主席咪又係習總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24780b90d7a574a17850d415e8cad21880af9db","tid":572276,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"下著一盤得大的棋"},{"pid":"3e254790c2fea4c0e76f009c08031417c7a4a9ee","tid":572276,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e405a206ff3107d01a0560186476c93e2331b5e","tid":572276,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:21:27.000Z","msg":"今次堅係登基"},{"pid":"cd171600082ec9ac0e02b4d784517f0cad0884a3","tid":572276,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"東廠都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bea34b7b1d4c04602327406076a7069ae9ffe71","tid":572276,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd171600082ec9ac0e02b4d784517f0cad0884a3","tid":572276,"uid":5045